      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">XS0504</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The constant &apos;variable&apos; cannot be marked static</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">If a variable is const, it is also static. If you want a const and static variable, just declare that variable as const; if all you want is a static variable, just mark it static.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The following sample generates XS0504:</text></para>
